{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_52_02",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 2話 美味しい山ご飯をご馳走するから",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "――で、突然部屋に押しかけてきて\n相談ってなんですか？　遙子さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—So‚ you suddenly barged into my room.\nWhat did you want to talk about‚ Haruko-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.9010883649
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "その……実はね、この旅行中に\nやってみたいことがあるから、手を貸してほしいのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… actually‚ during this trip‚\nthere’s something I want to try‚ and I’d like your help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "手伝うのは構いませんが……\n一体何をやりたいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t mind helping‚ but…\nwhat exactly do you want to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.5028117656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく山梨に来たでしょ？　だから、山梨の大自然の\n中でプチバーベキューしたいな～なんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We came all the way to Yamanashi‚ right? So‚ in the great outdoors of Yamanashi‚\nI was thinking it’d be nice to have a small barbecue or something…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.5059634685
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "それで、使い捨ての小さなバーベキューコンロを買って\n山の頂上でバーベキューをしようと思ったんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I bought a small disposable barbecue grill‚\nthinking we could have a barbecue at the top of the mountain.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに一人で道具と食材を全部担いで\n山登りするのは大変でしょ？　だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But carrying all the equipment and ingredients by myself\nwhile climbing a mountain would be tough‚ right? So…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0039026333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、荷物持ちに男手がほしいんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see—you want a man to carry the luggage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5330152989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.5330152989
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "荷物持ちってだけじゃないのよ？\n{user}君なら気心も知れてるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not just about carrying luggage‚ you know?\nWe know each other so well‚ {user}-kun‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.0266655128
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "最近は私の仕事について来てくれることも減ったから\n久しぶりに二人で積もる話もしたいなーなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and lately you haven’t been coming along to my work as much‚\nso I thought it’d be nice to catch up properly‚ just the two of us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺も遙子さんとゆっくり話したかったので\n喜んで手伝わせてもらいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wanted to take some time to talk with you too‚ Haruko-san‚\nso I’ll be happy to help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.2489881893,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.653467989
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう！　お礼に美味しい山ご飯を\nご馳走するから、楽しみにしててね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you! As a reward‚ I’ll treat you to\nsome delicious mountain food‚ so you can look forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.9448284309
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.9448284309
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 75.4614950975
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "スーパーにとうちゃ～く！　まずは食材の買い出しね\n地元の新鮮な食材を、一杯買っちゃうわよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re at the supermarket~! First‚ let’s shop for ingredients.\nWe’re gonna buy up lots of fresh local produce~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.1717214745
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君も食べたいものがあれば\nどんどんかごに入れてね！　遠慮はしなくていいから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If there’s anything you want to eat‚ {user}-kun‚\njust keep putting it in the basket! No need to hold back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "楽しそうですね……でも買い過ぎはダメですよ\nあんまり沢山買い込むと行きが大変になりますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem excited… but we shouldn’t buy too much.\nIf we buy too much‚ the climb will be rough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.5195446493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "はーい！　バーベキューと言えばやっぱりお肉よね……\nここは奮発して、ちょっとお高いステーキを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okaaay! When it comes to barbecues‚ meat is a must‚ right…\nLet’s splurge a bit and get some pricier steaks…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.6322203797
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "山梨は魚も美味しいのよ。脂の乗ったサーモンを\n炭火焼きにして皮はパリッ、中はふっくら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yamanashi also has great fish. Fatty salmon‚\ngrilled over charcoal—crispy skin‚ fluffy inside…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "新鮮な野菜も欠かせないわよね。バーベキューに\n合うのはピーマン、パプリカ、ししとう、にんじん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fresh vegetables are essential too. For barbecues‚\nbell peppers‚ paprika‚ shishito peppers‚ carrots…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.2390062494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "アツアツのトマトにトロトロのチーズを乗せて……\nホクホクのじゃがいもにバターもたまらないわ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "hot tomatoes topped with melty cheese…\nand fluffy potatoes with butter—irresistible!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.3636089805
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "くっ、なんて美味しそうな……分かりました\n重い物は俺が持ちますから、全部買いましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ghh‚ that all sounds incredible… fine.\nI’ll carry the heavy stuff‚ so let’s buy everything!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.5797893032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ありがとう。あとは食後のデザートに\n山梨名産のフルーツを……ああっ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ thank you. And for dessert after the meal‚\nYamanashi’s specialty fruits… aah!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.3994455888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.2409102285
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "見て！　こんな所にお酒のコーナーがあるわ！\nしかもスーパーとは思えない充実した品揃え……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look! There’s an alcohol section here!\nAnd such an amazing selection for a supermarket…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.4164203171
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、綺麗な景色を見ながら、バーベキューをつまみに\n美味しいお酒なんて最高の贅沢だと思わない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ don’t you think enjoying delicious drinks\nwhile snacking on barbecue and admiring the scenery is the ultimate luxury?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.9716062985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "最高の贅沢です！　……でも食材に加えて\nその重そうな酒瓶まで担いで山を登るのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The ultimate luxury indeed! …But on top of the ingredients‚\ncarrying those heavy bottles up the mountain will be…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.5330966357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 187.2093275869
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん私も持つわ！　あ、この地酒、美味しそう……\nでもこっちの純米吟醸も気になる……ああっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I’ll carry some too! Oh‚ this local sake looks good…\nBut this junmai ginjo is tempting too… ah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.1756137058
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "見て、ここの棚は全部ワインだわ！　そういえば山梨は\n国内産の約三割を生産するワインの名産地だったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look‚ this whole shelf is wine! Come to think of it‚ Yamanashi\nis a famous wine region‚ producing about 30% of Japan’s domestic wine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "地元の美味しいぶどうから作られた山梨ワイン……\nこれは飲まない訳にはいかないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yamanashi wine made from delicious local grapes…\nthere’s no way we can not drink this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 220.6486973926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "また荷物が……。でも、遙子さんのこんなに嬉しそうな\n笑顔が見られるなら、頑張り甲斐もあるか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "More luggage again… but seeing you so happy‚ Haruko-san‚\nmakes it worth the effort…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 229.5408192163
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "食材とお酒でかご一杯になっちゃったわね\nさすがにちょっと買い過ぎかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The basket’s full of ingredients and alcohol now.\nMaybe we did buy a bit too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 235.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "今日くらい羽目を外してもいいんじゃないですか？\nじゃあ、会計してきます。お金は俺が払いますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t it okay to splurge a little today?\nI’ll go take care of the bill—this one’s on me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 241.5988987291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 245.6251459286
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "え、でも、言い出したのは私なんだから\nお金は私が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? But this was my idea‚ so\nI should pay…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 249.4446723339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "日頃の感謝を伝えるための旅行ですから。遙子さんに\n喜んでもらえるなら、これくらい安い出費ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This trip is to show my appreciation. If it makes you happy‚ Haruko-san‚\nthen this is a small price to pay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 258.9990911012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_02-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "もう……かっこいいこと言っちゃって\nそれじゃ、今日は君の厚意に甘えちゃおうかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on… saying such cool things…\nThen I’ll accept your kindness today.",
        "id": ""
      },
